      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive preservation. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care. This is a collector-grade opportunity offering peerless performance and aesthetic perfection. We welcome any inspection to confirm its unrivaled status.",
